fields.name: Book Hugger : Curious Cat - Bookmark in metal
fields.description: Mark your place with this cute, custom-tooled metal bookmark! Our Curious Cat uses its tail to keep your place as it awaits your return to your favorite book. A unique book accessory! Suitable for gift-giving. Purr-fect for every book-loving cat person you know! Fun black metal bookmark is packaged in a clear plastic protective sleeve. Sleeve measures 6x21 cm.

fields.name: Curled up corners : Sleepy Owl - Bookmark in metal
fields.description:
Metal bookmark to put in the corners of the book. Better than dog ears!
Curl up with a good book and a charming metal animal bookmark. Made in brass with antique effect plated finishes and simple etched detail, the set comprises of a drowsy dog, cosy cat, quiet mouse, furled fox and a sleepy owl. Clips smoothly onto the corner of your favourite book to keep your place for next time. What could be more snug for an evening’s relaxing read?

fields.name: Luxury metal bookmark - William Morris Cray
fields.description: Luxury metal bookmark Cray. Silver-plated brass, William Morris design Cray in giclee print and covered with a domed dome. Tassel in matching color. William Morris started designing wallpaper and fabrics in 1862. His sources were planted themselves, observed in his gardens or on country walks, and also floral imagery in 16th-century woodcuts, illuminated manuscripts, tapestries, and other textiles. Solid brass, electro-plated with non-tarnishing silver finish, giclee print, domed dimensions: approx. 2,5 cm width x 9 cm length. Packaged in an acetate sleeve with a provenance card. Made in United States of America.

fields.name: Literary Emporium : Hamlet To read or not to read - Brass Bookmark
fields.description:
A skull-shaped bookmark inspired by Shakespeare's Hamlet. This bookmark is delicately engraved with a playful take on the iconic Hamlet quote! To read or not to read, that is the question. The bookmark can be slipped onto the page of your book to ensure you never lose your page. Both practical and unique, this brass bookmark makes a stylish and functional gift for any booklover. The bookmark is presented on a backing card, ready to give as a gift. Etched Brass (etched on both sides of the bookmark)
8 x 9 x 0.5 cm.

fields.name: Bumble & Birch : Books, because reality is overrated - Wooden bookmark with tassel
fields.description:
Add a touch of nature to your next novel with these beautiful eco-friendly wooden bookmarks. This engraved moon phase bookmark calls to nature lovers, adventurers, and outdoor lovers alike.
All bookmarks are engraved in-house using a durable unfinished beech hardwood. After your bookmark are engraved, they are finished with a black bookmark tassel. Best of all, this product is all-natural!
Bookmark dimensions:
Length - 12,5 cm
Width - 4 cm
Each bookmark is lovingly made in the small Colorado-based shop of Bumble & Birch. Edges will have a darkened look to them due to the laser cutting process. Due to the properties of natural wood, products may vary slightly in grain pattern or color.

fields.name: Fly Paper Products : Bee Quiet...I'm Reading - Wooden bookmark
fields.description:
A stylish and eco friendly way to hold your place while enjoying a good book! Each bookmark is made from 100% real, unaltered and natural wood materials. The production of the materials uses very minimal amounts of energy, gas and no use of water. This green and revolutionary product is made entirely in the USA. Since the wood is 100% natural, the card will biodegrade.
Dimensions: 5x15 cm. Made in USA by Fly Paper Products.

fields.name: Reading Light - Floral
fields.description:
NOTE: The lamp clip should only be threaded onto the book, not bent or opened!
Book Lover's Reading Light - Book lovers are NOT boring! So why should reading lights be dull?
This lovely little pocket sized lights are anything but. Of course they have all the same features that you would expect from a 'proper' book light such as a good battery life, dimmable LED (2 actually) bulbs, a secure clip and bendy positionable neck...just in a much nicer form and giftable packaging.
Designed especially to appeal to book lovers who appreciate the finer things in life and like a bit of colour in their reading lives. These will brighten up any book and are a fab unique gift!
Takes 1 x AAA battery in an easy to change compartment. Battery included!
With adjustable light settings and flexible neck - find your own comfy reading position.

Attaches with clip and can be rotated 360°. Charged with USB cable that is included.
Power: USB CHARGING. Height (cm): 6. Width (cm): 3.8. Depth (cm): 1.8. Weight (g): 111. Material: ABS, aluminium.

fields.name: Libri_x : Rechargeable LED reading light with touch switch - White
fields.description:
Rechargeable LED reading lamp from German Moses Verlag. 16 LED lights in the lamp head and three brightness settings together provide the perfect light for the purpose. The lamp is turned on and the brightness is regulated with a convenient touch switch. Flexible arm and clamp that can also be used as a lamp base. The lamp is charged with a USB-C cable (not included due to environmental concerns!)
4 hours charging time. Lights for 3-10 hours depending on the dimming level. Total length of the lamp 30 cm.

Soft coated barrel - A lovely thing to hold and behold. Black ball point pen containing superior German ink. It’s just a pen. But it IS a good one. It contains superior German black ink so flows beautifully and the barrel is lovely and soft coated to make it comfortable to hold.
